{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place a bowl onto mixing bowl lid and weigh in pistachios, granola and sage and set aside.","Place Parmesan cheese into mixing bowl and grate <nobr>10 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place rice into mixing bowl and grind <nobr>5 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Transfer ground rice into simmering basket and set aside.","Place yams, 1 oz butter and ½ tsp salt and water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket with ground rice and cook <nobr>15 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1.5<\/nobr>.","Set Varoma dish into position, place kale into Varoma dish, sprinkle with 1 tsp salt, secure Varoma lid and steam <nobr>5 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1.5<\/nobr>. Meanwhile heat a saucepan over medium-high heat. Add 2 oz butter, stirring until slightly brown. Remove pan from heat, continue stirring while adding reserved pistachio-granola mixture just until incorporated. Set pan aside.","Remove Varoma, remove simmering basket with spatula and set both aside.","Blend yams <nobr>5 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Add reserved steamed rice. <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong> and without measuring cup whip <nobr>40 sec\/\/speed 1.5<\/nobr>, while adding 2 oz butter, reserved grated Parmesan cheese, mascarpone and reserved steamed kale through hole in mixing bowl lid. Adjust seasoning to taste.","Divide Yam Porridge into four bowls, sprinkle with reserved Brown Butter Sage Crumble and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 oz unsalted pistachios, shelled","2 oz granola","1 oz fresh sage leaves, finely chopped","1 oz Parmesan cheese, in pieces","4 oz sushi rice","16 oz yams, peeled, cubed (½ in.), (approx. 1 lg. yam)","5 oz unsalted butter, divided","1 ½ tsp salt, divided, plus extra to season, to taste","28 oz water","½ bunch kale, sliced into strips (½ in.), stalks removed","8 oz mascarpone","freshly ground black pepper, to taste"]}],"id":"r412667","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-crsSbzREKws\/XZWZ2GP1RqI\/AAAAAAAAeSQ\/RDhsYPpc6xoOz1NzG89z7EIupALpR5K0QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_mBbbbwIjMXfX7Ex7.png","title":"Yam Porridge with Brown Butter Sage Crumble (Tim Hollingsworth)","publishedAt":"2019-03-29T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{},"usefulItems":"saucepan, stove top","hintsAndTricks":["To view Chef Tim Hollingsworth prepare this dish: https:\/\/vimeo.com\/251745356"],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","40m","4 portions"]}